WEBVTT


01:20:57.811 --> 01:20:59.145 line:85.83%,end
It's not over.

01:20:59.771 --> 01:21:02.649 line:85.83%,end
The eyes of the first person you kill
will haunt you forever.

01:21:03.483 --> 01:21:05.902 line:85.83%,end
The eyes of the person
whose life slips away…

01:21:06.486 --> 01:21:07.904 line:85.83%,end
will follow you around

01:21:08.947 --> 01:21:10.323 line:85.83%,end
when you eat or sleep.

01:21:11.032 --> 01:21:12.409 line:85.83%,end
Even

01:21:13.326 --> 01:21:15.203 line:85.83%,end
in your dreams.

01:21:50.655 --> 01:21:51.489 line:85.83%,end
You know…

01:21:52.240 --> 01:21:55.452 line:85.83%,end
To tell the truth,
this isn't any ordinary coffee.

01:21:59.789 --> 01:22:00.957 line:85.83%,end
If you drink it,

01:22:03.585 --> 01:22:06.796 line:85.83%,end
all your bad memories will be erased.

01:22:15.722 --> 01:22:17.682 line:85.83%,end
Why are you laughing? I'm serious.

01:22:20.060 --> 01:22:23.146 line:85.83%,end
Whenever something bad happened,
I drank this and erased those memories.

01:22:26.149 --> 01:22:27.943 line:85.83%,end
What should I erase today?

01:22:29.069 --> 01:22:30.403 line:85.83%,end
What should I erase?

01:22:40.413 --> 01:22:44.501 line:85.83%,end
I just erased the memories
of me singing at Evergreen Records.

01:22:56.054 --> 01:22:58.139 line:85.83%,end
Hey. Stop laughing.

01:22:58.723 --> 01:23:01.851 line:85.83%,end
Come on. I said I just erased them.

01:23:02.727 --> 01:23:04.104 line:85.83%,end
But I didn't.

01:23:07.482 --> 01:23:10.068 line:85.83%,end
-Then drink it and erase them now.
-I don't want to.

01:23:10.360 --> 01:23:12.779 line:85.83%,end
But you should.

01:23:12.862 --> 01:23:14.197 line:85.83%,end
I don't want to.

01:23:17.617 --> 01:23:18.451 line:85.83%,end
Darn it.

01:23:33.717 --> 01:23:35.385 line:85.83%,end
After you left,

01:23:36.344 --> 01:23:40.348 line:85.83%,end
you didn't call once,
so I was upset and hated you for it.

01:23:41.766 --> 01:23:42.934 line:85.83%,end
I just erased it.

01:24:27.103 --> 01:24:29.397 line:85.83%,end
I held a gun to your head.

01:24:36.112 --> 01:24:37.530 line:85.83%,end
I erased the memory.

01:25:11.981 --> 01:25:12.982 line:85.83%,end
That memory…

01:25:20.615 --> 01:25:22.242 line:85.83%,end
I erased it as well.

